<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Pixel Play - Nostalgia meets Futuristic Automation</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Futuristic tech meets retro arcade. Coiner automates and monetizes real machines with seamless scans and payments." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <header class="site-header" role="banner">
    <div class="container nav-wrap">
      <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="Pixel Play Home">
        Pixel Play
      </a>
      <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Main Navigation">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#hero">Hero</a></li>
          <li><a href="#featured-in">Featured In</a></li>
          <li><a href="#coiner-system">Coiner System</a></li>
          <li><a href="#signup">Sign Up</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <a href="#signup" class="cta" aria-label="Sign Up">
        Sign Up (CTA)
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section id="hero" class="hero" aria-label="Hero">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1>Powered by Nostalgia</h1>
      <p class="tagline">
        Futuristic tech meets retro arcade, automation system and everyday machines.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-visual" aria-label="Hero Visual">
        <!-- Placeholder image or SVG; replace with your artwork -->
        <img src="path/to/hero-visual.png" alt="Futuristic tech meets retro arcade" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured In -->
  <section id="featured-in" class="featured" aria-label="Featured In">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Featured In</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Mizoram’s first automation system • Mizoram’s Inventors Challenge - No. 1</p>
      <!-- Add logos or badges as needed -->
      <div class="featured-logos" aria-label="Featured logos">
        <!-- Example placeholders -->
        <span class="badge">mizoram</span>
        <span class="badge">inventors challenge</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Coiner System -->
  <section id="coiner-system" class="coiner" aria-label="Coiner System">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Coiner System</h2>

      <div class="coiner-grid">
        <article class="coiner-item" aria-label="Integration">
          <h3>integration</h3>
          <p>Arcades, laundromats, photobooths, parking systems, or anything that needs to start, unlock, or run on time. If it is a real machine, Coiner can plug into it.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="coiner-item" aria-label="Automation">
          <h3>automation</h3>
          <p>Once it is connected, Coiner runs the machine automatically. Start, unlock, time, switch modes—whatever the device needs. No staff babysitting. Your customer just scans and pays. Coiner does the rest.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="coiner-item" aria-label="Collect Payment">
          <h3>collect payment</h3>
          <p>Payments trigger actions instantly and you can track earnings. Simple for users, clean for operators. Set it up once, then let the machine run itself.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sign Up Form -->
  <section id="signup" class="signup" aria-label="Sign Up">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>It's almost here. Be among the first.</h2>
      <p>By entering your name and email address we will reach out to you the moment our pre-order process opens up. We’ll never share your information with third-party marketing services.</p>

      <form action="/preorder" method="post" class="signup-form" autocomplete="on" aria-label="Pre-order sign up">
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Type your name here" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Type your email here" required />
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="button">Sign up</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
    <div class="container footer-content">
      <div class="footer-brand">Pixel Play</div>
      <address>
        Aizawl, Mizoram, India
      </address>
      <div class="socials" aria-label="Social Media">
        <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">
          Instagram
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
